node.text:
My Epilepsy Warrior üíú #EpilepsyAwarenessDay
Today it‚Äôs #PurpleDay, a day to raise awareness for those with epilepsy. As you might know by now, Loulou has suffered from epileptic seizures for 1.5 years, which have gotten worse over time. The past 6 months have been intense, but I am so amazed by how quickly Loulou is back on her (wobbly) ‚Äúpaws‚Äù and is her happy self again. Things are pretty uncertain still at the moment as we‚Äôre hoping the new seizure meds will work for Loulou, but knowing how strong Loulou is gives me hope. 
Sending extra love to my fellow ‚ÄòPurple Pugs‚Äô @lil_pickles_da_pug and @pugridesshotgun and every other Epilepsy Warrior out there today üíú
